\pard\f0\fs28 Variable in habit, leaf-shape and inflorescence. Especially in the E. Mediterranean region, variants with a less compact inflorescence occur, which have been called var. {\i serpentini} G. Beck and var.{\i  sparsiflora} Schur. Such plants may deserve subspecific recognition.
