\pard\f0\fs28 Sect. ELISANTHE (Fenzl) Fenzl (Sect.{\i  Melandriformes }(Boiss.) Chowdhuri). Annuals, biennials or perennials with large flowers, solitary or in dichasia; dioecious (except {\b 128}). Petal-limb bifid; coronal scales prominent; claw auriculate; styles 5 (3 in 128). Capsule without basal septa, dehiscing with 6 or 10 teeth; carpophore very short.
